stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle

  state Processing {
    [*] --> Validating
    Validating --> Computing
    Computing --> Formatting
    Formatting --> [*]
  }

  Idle --> Processing : start
  Processing --> Idle : complete
  Processing --> Error : fail

  state fork_state <<fork>>
  state join_state <<join>>

  Idle --> fork_state
  fork_state --> TaskA
  fork_state --> TaskB
  TaskA --> join_state
  TaskB --> join_state
  join_state --> Complete

  Error --> [*]
  Complete --> [*]
